    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "b",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "White Sky:"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The wind has been rising steadily and now is blowing\nthe rain in huge sheets across the lake. Swelling tributary streams\nthreaten to overtake the shoreline. Animals and villagers alike flee to\nsafety lest they be caught in the flood."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "b",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Kobo\u2019s Market:"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "From far off you can hear shouts of alarm. You can\njust make out the dell that holds Kobo\u2019s Market through the driving\nrain. The water around the main structure is already knee deep,\nand you can see Ren Kobo\u2019s porters saving what goods they can,\nretreating to the upper balcony."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "b",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Golden Shore:"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Tributary streams north of the shoreline have begun\nto spill their banks, becoming a boiling sluice of brown water among\nthe pines. If the water isn\u2019t redirected, it could wash out long stretches\nof the shoreline and carry away dozens, or even hundreds, of trees."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "b",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\u00bb Continue reading:"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "em",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Divert the flood by clearing beings and features while they have a Flood card attached."
                }
              ],
              "color": "blue"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Set up the new location, refresh, and draw path cards for the new round, then perform the following based on how many days have passed since starting this mission:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "b",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "0:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Search the General set for two Flood cards, and shuffle them into the path deck."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "b",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "1:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Search the General set for two Flood cards, and shuffle one into the path deck. Then attach the other Flood card to the being or feature from the path deck that is in play with the highest presence."
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
